# Project Blueprint

Last refreshed: 2026-03-09 (Phase 4 verification, full-enhance run `20260309-205940-full-enhance`).

## Scope
- Target project: `/Users/macbook/Desktop/Huz`
- Scope level: `multi-panel-fullstack`
- Surfaces mapped in this refresh:
  - `Huz-Backend` (Django 5 monolith)
  - `Huz-Web-Frontend` (public/user React app)
  - `Huz-Admin-Frontend` (super-admin + partner panel React app)
  - `Huz-Operator-Frontend` (operator React app)

## Architecture Overview
- Backend is a modular Django monolith exposing REST endpoints across six route groups: `/api/v1`, `/common`, `/partner`, `/bookings`, `/management`, `/chat`.
- Frontend surfaces are split by audience:
  - `Huz-Web-Frontend`: website discovery and user booking lifecycle.
  - `Huz-Admin-Frontend`: super-admin approvals and partner/admin panel flows.
